Package be.kdg.rentalVehicleProject.model

Class RentalVehicle

java.lang.Object
be.kdg.rentalVehicleProject.model.RentalVehicle
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<RentalVehicle>
public class RentalVehicle extends Object implements Comparable<RentalVehicle>
The RentalVehicle class represents a rental vehicle with various properties such as model, rental price per day, number of persons it can accommodate, vehicle type, manufacture date, and vehicle registration number. For more information about rental vehicles, see: RentalVehicle on Wikipedia
Version:
1.0
Author:
Said Khalaf
